snippet.title: Legend of Iya Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the trailer for my campaign to kickstarter the crap out of LOI.

http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/523651724/legend-of-iya Please support the project here.

http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=159562434 Steam Greenlight link!

And now you can actually play the demo:
http://www.sendspace.com/file/ohlmuf
